com.google.api.data.client.v2.atom
Annotation Type DefaultNamespaceAlias

Deprecated. 

@Target(value=TYPE)
@Retention(value=RUNTIME)
@Deprecated
public @interface DefaultNamespaceAlias

Use this annotation to specify the default namespace alias to use when the Name annotation is missing from the fields in this type or if the namespace alias is missing from the value of the Name annotation. This overrides for the fields in this type the what has been specified as the general default "" namespace.
